RICHERT, Respondent, v. BACKENSTROSS, Appellant. (Supreme Court General Term, Fourth Department. December 8, 1893.) Action by Alexander Richert against John Baekenstross.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Decision as stated in memorandum of HARDIN, P. J., filed with the clerk of Onondaga. See 24 N. Y. Supp. 1009.
